6:
From now on, I wanna do bigger and
better shows!
9:
In my humble opinion, that show
you crashed the other day was
already plenty spectacular.

anything new to show off! It was
missing an extra bit of OOMPH!

But I can't figure out what exactly
that oomph needed to be...

115:
How about another
performance?
It's show time!
118:
What a wonderful show it was... I'm
so moved... I think my back is about
to give out!
124:
Actually, I got something out of it
tooI just had an epiphany while

Gramps, can I get you and the other

something?
131: Hey, it's the lady from the other day!
132:
Is she going to perform for us

Honestly speaking, I'm surprised the

137:
Yeah? Fans tend to do whatever

143:
We've got some special guests
behind the scenes today. They're
gonna help me put on a summer

150:
In the name of the light... and the
twinkling stars above, I deliver this
spectacle to all!
165:
The power of light is meant to
banish darkness and destroy evil,
but the light of her heart is even
more
171:
Stop thinking so hard and just enjoy
the moment, Light.

I want to thank everyone for all your
help with today's performance!
183:
From the wonderful people I met on
this island...
184:
To the friends who helped me come
up with the whole shebang!
188:
And let's not forget the most
important crowdevery one of you

Now, sit back and keep watching,
